Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像也會很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好小奏說不穿袴也行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 穿那個的話會死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘帶東西吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和團體戰不同 個人戰是沒有預賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加人數會有四百多人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨同學是A級
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島和西田同學是B級
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駒野和大江同學是D級
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家分散在不同的地方進行比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過面對著全國各地的對手 大家盡情挑戰自己的實力吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們是對手哦 書桌小子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會輸的!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標也是拿下B級的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦真島 你沒什麼幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:00:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B級的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能和B級的人比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:11.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\fn楷体\shad0\bord0\blur7\t(0,1383,\blur0)\fad(1383,0)\c&H5A5D76&}下次在比賽中見 新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:29.55,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(817,811)\pos(490,211)}願得厚意報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:29.55,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(817,811)\pos(394,295)}惟君知我心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查看過比賽安排卡後 請對號入座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽對手是鹿兒島的花本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是個怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 須藤!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王也參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個 第一場和我們學校的甘糟同學比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宮詩暢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學四年級就已經成為了A級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都的高中一年級學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是史上最年輕的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在近江神宮擦肩而過的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天果然還是打扮得好土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T恤還塞進褲子裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是她風格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥印個雪人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明長得挺可愛的 卻又不負眾望地土氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須藤 你也參加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 女王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別叫我什麼女王啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一場的對手不是須藤 我還鬆了口氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團體戰沒能入圍 卻還來參加個人戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是很喜歡歌留多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 要是在比賽中遇上的話 還請手下留情~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我宰了你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是赤裸裸的挖苦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要把你打得落花流水!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報了預選賽的一箭之仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「女王」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本女性中最厲害的歌留多選手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是怎樣搶牌的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多強呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點贏下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看女王的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:54.93,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…と さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…又將至 再綻此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たきのおとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「飛練余枯影…」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.13,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こひすてふ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「春情初凝成…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.48,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あしびきの…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「山鳥耀垂尾…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想快點贏下來? 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的人可都是A級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 得集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更謹慎地記牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精力集中在每一張牌上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.32,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なつのよは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「仲夏夜未央…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是北央的甘糟 還贏了24張?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…他只搶到了一張?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專用水壺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的還是熱水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在對第二場進行分組
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女王比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…但是又不想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把她打垮!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要遇到女王啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和她比…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和她比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想和她比!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟大江同學的媽媽借了攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要把大家的比賽都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗記時間 結束!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:13.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}なにわずに　さくやこのはな　ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:13.76,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「花映難波津 隆冬且暫隱」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位置在讀手的正對面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸氣的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:22.57,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:22.57,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又將至 再綻此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐氣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細聽 第一個音!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:31.78,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:31.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又將至 再綻此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:34.65,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「靜…」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.41,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…ととぎす
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…夜待子規」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢速回放都看不見?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:51.70,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ただありあけの　つきぞのこれる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:51.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「聞聲尋不見 惟得殘月白」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みかの…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「木津…」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.59,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…はら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…生瓶原」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.04,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あさぢ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「白茅…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像劃過真空的針一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聲音的歌留多!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是B級第二場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好分組以後 請對號入座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不戰而勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}淘汰賽或者大會中，若對手棄權，\N則產生不戰而勝的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島你太狡猾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想去給D級的小奏加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就一定得是大江同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小奏說過 「如果你的比賽先結束」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就來給我加油吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果你要去看D級比賽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她我想跟她說「小奏加油!」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宮…詩暢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟女王對戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 根本搞不清發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也能看懂的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨陣地裡的牌 一張都沒減少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:13.49,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みよしのの　やまのあきかぜ　さよふけて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋風肅吉野 時逝榮華更」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:25.22,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふるさとさむく　ころもうつなり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「夜闌空寂寥 惟聞搗衣聲」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.71,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おおえやま…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大江連生野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好快! 那是什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到什麼都看不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牌讀出之後的出手動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千早更快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到「おお」 就去進攻敵陣的「初入」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.73,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(900,658)}おほけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使己陣的「大江」是對應牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.14,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}おおえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姿勢也能完美地倒回來搶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王一直聽到「大江」讀完才出手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.34,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}おおえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能趕上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等到聽完才出手?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.00,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はなさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「山風…」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:12.54,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…そふ　あらしのにはの　ゆきならで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…邀櫻散 若雪妝庭來」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這戰況 又來了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經差了十張了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宮詩暢 果然等級不同啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做對手的那女生好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生也快喪失鬥志了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也不弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該能以不遜於女王的速度 搶下她盯上的牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是場上的牌有幾十張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法把全場的都盯住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…難道說女王能做到嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是女王 也不可能全無破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如那邊的「羈旅」和「葦生」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.03,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,658)}なにはえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.03,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(840,658)}なにはが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為「與君」已經讀過了 聽到「なに」就可以一起掃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.67,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,658)}なにし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她卻沒分開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒盡早分開 真是不可理喻!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位置是任我隨便搶啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搶到!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩張一起搶掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太容易被看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.07,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わすらるる…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「海約已相違…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.11,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありまやま…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「豬名近有馬…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是因為你只盯著某幾張牌啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很想搶下第一張牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有喪失鬥志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家看看你的進攻型歌留多吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:27.91,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}なに…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:27.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「葦…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:35.57,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}…はが た　みじかきあしの　ふしのまも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:35.57,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「…生難波灘 節短聚益稀」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 真島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是哪邊搶到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在很難弄清楚吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連選手們自己都弄不清楚的時候 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要聽裁判的 或者雙方自行磋商
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 越是高等級的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就越是看得清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是抱著「掃走那兩張」的心態出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是女王她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻靠的是「只掃那一點」的敏銳度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其想著守住己陣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如將意識的重心一直放在敵陣深處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已經進攻了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有其他的武器了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達迪熊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}這是改自泰迪熊吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 什麼? 是指這件T恤嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的T恤是…雪人丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在大阪才有官方商店 這邊要郵購才買得到的雪人丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把水桶拿下來就會露出髮髻的超可愛角色!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃迷人之處!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 比賽比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她是女王 但也是跟我同年的16歲女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能贏不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:17.22,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}あはでこのよを　すぐしてよとや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:17.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「怨君心何忍 殘生會無期」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よのなかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「世間千般愁…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了嗎 剛才那下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是怎麼回事? 動作很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…那個是「圍手」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「圍手」?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的陣裡是「世間」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.28,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(760,658)}よのなかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陣裡的是「粗纜」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:39.26,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(750,658)}よのなかは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定字很長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道「よのなか」後面的音是「は」還是「よ」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在讀到之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手圍住牌不讓對方搶到的技巧 就叫做「圍手」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們都圍住了己陣的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對應牌是千早陣中的「世間」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.91,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(810,658)}よのなかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以接下來她只要按住牌就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在千早按住牌之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的手搶先一步從僅有的少許縫隙間…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想像自己獲勝的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種就叫「公開處刑」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想對上她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 連一張都搶不到就敗陣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:41.77,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}やまのおくにも しかぞなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:41.77,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「循山覓幽隱 鹿鳴復添傷」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張數相差越多 攻擊式歌留多就越不利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以概率來看 出現在己陣的對應牌就自然會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心態會轉變為「防守」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.62,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}わがいほは…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「草廬坐東南…」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 以那份對己陣的擅長來看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的是防守型歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻難有成效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也只能進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持住啊 千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.71,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おほけなく…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初入比睿門…」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不進攻?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一開始都是幹勁滿滿地來挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟女王對戰 我要贏下她爆個冷門!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之後 就會變得像只有我一個人在玩歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正我也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是早點結束掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相差15張?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨同學 加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我以往的歌留多打法 連一張都搶不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事還是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要搶到一張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一張…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要搶到!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰況不利的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須藤好像會站起來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要一副很拽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道女王是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左撇子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 我居然現在才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是有多緊張多慌亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能在拼勁上 輸給12歲時候的我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能持續多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:21.23,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わがたつそまに　すみぞめのそで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但展墨染袖 苦世澤佛恩」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.06,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かぜをいたみ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「萬浪奔捲去…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻後又倒回來搶了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相上下 是哪邊搶到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我進攻之後倒回己陣的速度相比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆直進攻的女王會更快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我學的是進攻型歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 想想就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當對自己的防守很有信心的人 其己陣的深處被攻下時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多麼大的打擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰況就是靠這樣扭轉過來的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:07.05,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くだけてものを　おもふころかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我心向伊處 腸斷情亦摧」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.88,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにはえの…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「羈旅與君會…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說不相上下嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一張!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是同時搶到 所以算是你搶到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}同時搶到則算牌所在\N陣地的一方搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?! 收下啦 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般是不會退回去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的牌都是自己的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上不能認輸 要堅持說是自己搶到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了在原田老師的理念中絕對不能做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡 可是近江勸學館
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名人戰也好 女王戰也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣是在這張榻榻米上進行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想靠僥倖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從她手上搶下的第一張牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會帶我走向一月時的那個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:10.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(600,600)\fn楷体\bord0\shad0\c&H537683&}小倉百人一首 歌留多 名人女王決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:30.58,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みをつくしてや　こひわたるべき
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「難波蘆節短 長戀此生銷」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:35.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枯…」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:43.33,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}…くからに　あきのくさきの　しをるれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:43.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「…風遠山至 草折百茆蕭」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶到了女王慣用手那一邊的…一字決定牌!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王居然在一字決定牌上輸給別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是在「枯風遠山至」的「枯」念出來的同時掃掉的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:54.78,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,658)}ふくからに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:54.78,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,658)}ふ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田老師說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說千早能聽到完整的「FU」出現前的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:05.03,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,658)}ふ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出聲前的瞬間 那輕微的F聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枯風遠山至」 也是千早擅長的牌啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:15.09,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,658)}ふくからに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一張…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張牌 又成為了我搶下的第一張
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:49.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,むべやまかぜを　あらしといふらむ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「荻悲蘆摵摵 威名由此邀」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.93,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ちはやぶる…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「神代有蓬萊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速搶送牌!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}指剛剛送給對手的牌，馬上就搶到\N對於扭轉局面很有幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續兩張!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一張…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將帶我成為女王!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
